    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 987.1-generation Cayman S represents a pinnacle in mid-engine balance, powered by the 3.4L M97 flat-six engine featuring VarioCam Plus variable valve timing. The longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission offers precise gates and short-throw engagement, driving power through a rigid chassis with exceptional torsional stiffness. This example features the Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) system, providing active damping adjustment for varied road surfaces. Crucially, the intermediate shaft (IMS) bearing has been inspected and the rear main seal (RMS) replaced to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The braking system utilizes four-piston aluminum monoblock calipers over vented, cross-drilled rotors for consistent thermal management and fade resistance. A mechanically sound specimen for the discerning driver who prioritizes kinematic feedback and linear power delivery.",
