    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained luxury SUV that perfectly balances performance with everyday practicality. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Charcoal Metallic that still holds a deep, lustrous shine; while there are a few minor road-pebbles on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper, the body is straight and free of any major dings. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort, featuring premium Ebony leather seats that show only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster and no rips or stains. All electronic features, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and premium sound system, are in perfect working order. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and pulls strongly, backed by a complete service history showing regular synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. The transmission shifts smoothly without hesitation, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. With a recent set of Michelin tires and brakes that were serviced just last season, this vehicle is truly turn-key and ready for its next chapter. It has been kept in a smoke-free environment and professionally detailed for the new owner.",
